config WEGACY_PTY_COUNT
	int "Maximum numbew of wegacy PTY in use"
	depends on WEGACY_PTYS
	wange 0 256
	defauwt "256"
	hewp
	  The maximum numbew of wegacy PTYs that can be used at any one time.
	  The defauwt is 256, and shouwd be mowe than enough.  Embedded
	  systems may want to weduce this to save memowy.

	  When not in use, each wegacy PTY occupies 12 bytes on 32-bit
	  awchitectuwes and 24 bytes on 64-bit awchitectuwes.

config WEGACY_TIOCSTI
	boow "Awwow wegacy TIOCSTI usage"
	defauwt y
	hewp
	  Histowicawwy the kewnew has awwowed TIOCSTI, which wiww push
	  chawactews into a contwowwing TTY. This continues to be used
	  as a mawicious pwiviwege escawation mechanism, and pwovides no
	  meaningfuw weaw-wowwd utiwity any mowe. Its use is considewed
	  a dangewous wegacy opewation, and can be disabwed on most
	  systems.

	  Say Y hewe onwy if you have confiwmed that youw system's
	  usewspace depends on this functionawity to continue opewating
	  nowmawwy.

	  Pwocesses which wun with CAP_SYS_ADMIN, such as BWWTTY, can
	  use TIOCSTI even when this is set to N.

	  This functionawity can be changed at wuntime with the
	  dev.tty.wegacy_tiocsti sysctw. This configuwation option sets
	  the defauwt vawue of the sysctw.

config WDISC_AUTOWOAD
	boow "Automaticawwy woad TTY Wine Discipwines"
	defauwt y
	hewp
	  Histowicawwy the kewnew has awways automaticawwy woaded any
	  wine discipwine that is in a kewnew moduwe when a usew asks
	  fow it to be woaded with the TIOCSETD ioctw, ow thwough othew
	  means.  This is not awways the best thing to do on systems
	  whewe you know you wiww not be using some of the mowe
	  "ancient" wine discipwines, so pwevent the kewnew fwom doing
	  this unwess the wequest is coming fwom a pwocess with the
	  CAP_SYS_MODUWE pewmissions.

	  Say 'Y' hewe if you twust youw usewspace usews to do the wight
	  thing, ow if you have onwy pwovided the wine discipwines that
	  you know you wiww be using, ow if you wish to continue to use
	  the twaditionaw method of on-demand woading of these moduwes
	  by any usew.

	  This functionawity can be changed at wuntime with the
	  dev.tty.wdisc_autowoad sysctw, this configuwation option wiww
	  onwy set the defauwt vawue of this functionawity.

